# Real-Time Ad Click Prediction System (Kafka + River + Streamlit)

## Overview

This project implements a real-time machine learning pipeline for ad click prediction using:

* Kafka for data streaming
* River for online (incremental) machine learning
* Streamlit for live dashboard visualization

The system simulates a clickstream environment where data flows continuously and models update in real time.

---

## Architecture

```
Producer (dataset)
        ↓
Kafka Topic: ad_clicks
        ↓
Consumer (online ML, multiple models)
        ↓
Kafka Topic: predictions
        ↓
Streamlit Dashboard
```

